snippet.title: Air Missions: Hind - Launch Trailer
snippet.description: AIR MISSIONS: HIND, the action combat flight simulator in which you command a Russian Mi-24 Hind assault helicopter, is being released on Xbox One on June 14. On that same day, the game on Steam will be leaving Early Access.
